# TruffleHog path-exclude regex (one per line).
# Passed as `--exclude-paths` from the Validate workflow.

# Firebase web config — `apiKey: "AIzaSy..."` matches Google API-key detectors,
# but Firebase web keys are public-by-design project identifiers, not
# credentials. Backend access is gated by Firebase Admin SDK verifying ID
# tokens server-side.
src/lib/firebase/index\.ts$

# Local tooling state. Already gitignored, so CI never sees these — listed
# here so a local `trufflehog filesystem .` matches the CI behaviour.
^\.claude/
^\.claude-flow/
^\.serena/
^\.agents/
